dct_title_s: Southern Metropolitan area : [Hobart Metropolitan area (228, topographic map)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by isobaths. Topographic map showing cadastral boundaries. Map set covering Hobart and environs. Princeton Map Collection holds three maps of this set.
dct_creator_sm: Tasmania. Southern Metropolitan Master Planning Authority
dct_publisher_sm: [Hobart, Tas.] : Southern Metropolitan Master Planning Authority, 1963.
